# üêû bug report

### Affected Package
The issue is caused by package @angular 8.1.0


### Is this a regression?
Yes, the previous version in which this bug was not present was: 7.x


### Description
If you use AoT along with `strictMetadataEmit` enabled and have lazy loaded modules AoT build will throw an error.

## üî¨ Minimal Reproduction
Clone this repo https://github.com/pawelkondraciuk/angular8-example-app and run `ng serve --aot`

Nutshell:
```
// tsconfig.json
"angularCompilerOptions": {
  "strictMetadataEmit": true
},
```
```
// app-routing.module.ts
{path: '/', loadChildren: () => import('./modules/home/home.module').then(m => m.HomeModule)},
```

`ng serve --aot`

